page.title: 06BROWNIE GUIDES
page.content: I go to{Brownies}on a Tuesday night, from 6.30p.m. until 7.30p.m. Sometimes we bake things or play games, work or do activities. My six is called { {Sprites}and I am the seconder. I am in {1st Stainland Brownie Pack}at St.Andrew's church hall. We have 3 rangers, Brown Owl, Snowy Owl, and Little Owl and 2 guides. We have to pay 20p subs to our sixer who then gives it to Brown Owl. At brownies, my favourite activities are playing games and rounders. I enjoy brownies very much, so do my friends Rachel and Mandy who also go there.
